content: dc2950e94fd12022579c7307b63f779f eng UTF-8 Dataset Dataset Diane Love AZGS 520-209-4119 416 W Congress Tucson AZ 85701 diane.love@azgs.az.gov pointOfContact 2013-03-08T19:38:40Z ISO-USGIN 1.2 Idaho Oil and Gas Exploration Wells 2012-12-28T00:00:00 publication Roy Breckenridge Idaho Geological Survey 208-885-7992 875 Perimeter Drive MS 3014, Morrill Hall, University of Idaho Moscow ID 83844-3014 roybreck@uidaho.edu originator Dean Garwood Idaho Geological Survey 208-885-7992 875 Perimeter Drive MS 3014, Morrill Hall, University of Idaho Moscow ID 83844-3014 dgarwood@uidaho.edu originator This dataset is a compilation of oil and gas exploration wellheaders compiled by the Idaho Geological Survey, published as a Web feature service, a web map service, an ESRI service, and as a set of Excel worksheets for the National Geothermal Data System. The downloadable workbook contains 8 worksheets, including information about the template, notes related to revisions of the template, Resource provider information, the data, a field list (data mapping view) and a worksheet with vocabularies for use in populating the spreadsheet (data valid terms). Data from 148 oil and gas exploration wells are included. Data from 148 oil and gas exploration wells are included.
